<p>The Structure of a Summary list Must Follow this tag order:</p>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li>&lt;nhs-summary-list&gt;</li>
        <li>&lt;nhs-summary-list-row&gt;</li>
    </ul>
</p>
<p>This order is enforced by razor, and will throw a compiler error if you try to use it in a different way.</p>

